                                            </span>
                                            <span className="text-gray-500 text-xs ml-1">/ mois</span>
                                            <p className="text-xs text-emerald-600 mt-1">
                                                {formatPrice(price)} / an &middot; √âconomie de {formatPrice(savings)}
                                            </p>
